: 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\boxed{\beta=-\frac{J'_{m}(kR_{1})}{Y_{m}'(kR_{1})}=-\frac{J'_{m}(kR_{2})}{Y_{m}'(kR_{2})}}.
