\begin_layout Enumerate
At the origin, we can't blow up, and therefore we only have 
\begin_inset Formula $J$
\end_inset

 for 
\begin_inset Formula $r<R_{1}$
\end_inset

, but we have both 
\begin_inset Formula $J$
\end_inset

