\begin_inset Formula 
\[
u(r,\theta)=[A\cos(m\theta)+B\sin(m\theta)]\times\begin{cases}
\alpha J_{m}(k_{1}r) & r<R_{1}\\
\beta J_{m}(k_{2}r)+\gamma Y_{m}(k_{2}r) & r>R_{1}
\end{cases}.
\]

\end_inset

Note that the angular dependence must be the same for all 
\begin_inset Formula $r$
\end_inset

 in order to have continuity at 
\begin_inset Formula $r=R_{1}$
\end_inset

.
